For a photovoltaic system that is composed of a photovoltaic generator coupled with a resistive load, it requires to have a boost type converter. Its model is presented in Fig. 4 the direct current/direct current (DC/DC) boost converter will use an MPPT controller for the sake of maintaining the optimal output power. The corresponding system is described through a state equation with two sets that are depending on the switch state (SW). If it has a zero logic value (SW=0), the corresponding differential equation is given by 6\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
